# Copy to clumps/services/kafka/.env in hdc-private (or hdc root; never commit).
# Values are optional unless the package manifest declares env_required.

# Apache Kafka KRaft cluster (`clumps/services/kafka`) — cluster_id in config.json (no vault required for PLAINTEXT).
